1985;;Movers & Shakers;;American;;William Asher;;Walter Matthau, Charles Grodin, Tyne Daly;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Movers_%26_Shakers;;Hollywood studio mogul Joe Mulholland (Matthau) vows to produce the pet project of a dying acquaintance, who has been trying to find a way to make a film out of a best-selling sex manual. He and screenwriter Herb Derman (Grodin) try to make it happen, but fail in every possible way. Meanwhile, Herb is distracted by his own marital problems.